<b>What's new:</b>
<p>
<ul>
<li>changed "see inside magnet" feature [351]. Bar magnet is no longer transparent. 
Instead, a separate B-field is displayed that moves with the magnet.
As requested, the Options>FieldControls feature does not change the layout of this B-field.
<li>fixed divide-by-zero problem that occurs when the distance is zero between one of the bar magnet's poles and a point in the B-field grid [492]
</ul>
